<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            width: 90%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .content {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 10px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Welcome to FalconHive!</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <strong><%= username %></strong>,</p>
            <p>We are excited to inform you that your institution, <strong><%= institutionName %></strong>, has been successfully registered on the FalconHive Hospital Management System. As the administrator, you now have the ability to manage and oversee various activities within your institution.</p>
            <p>Below are your login credentials:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Email:</strong> <%= email %></li>
                <li><strong>Password:</strong> <%= password %></li>
            </ul>
            <p>Please log in to your account to start managing your institution's activities, including creating and managing departments, overseeing daily operations, and much more. For security reasons, we recommend changing your password upon your first login.</p>
            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, our support team is here to help.</p>
            <p>We look forward to supporting your institution's growth and success with FalconHive.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> FalconHive. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
